description:
NounsDAO Chinese celebrates the beauty of the Mandarin Chinese language and culture, globally. We hope to connect with friends from all over the world who speak and read in Chinese, and those who are learning it or wants to learn.

NounsDAO 中文版 庆祝全球普通话之美和文化。我们希望与世界各地会说和读中文的朋友，以及正在学习或想学习中文的人联系。

So excited to build together! We welcome everyone. ⌐◨-◨  很兴奋欢迎大家一起建NounsDAO 中文版。
